metadata.name: Street Soldiers
metadata.description:
Children of the Jamaican ghetto, unable to escape as they are bound to the streets. Bound by their duties to protect, hunt and kill for their families. 
In this case I've decided to use local street lights ( light post ) to connect them to the their communities. 

-J.H.A.G ( GraytArt )

Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgX0gyy0mkKFsuaJ9S4TtFQ/videos
